 Galvatron heard the thoughts of Megatron in his head. "We have barley any 
connections but one is reading the mind. You where not trapped. You where 
part of me. You where what drove we to finaly defeat Valtron. And for that I 
will always be gratefull." He looked behind to see LikeLike following. He 
thought the bot would be useful so he let it be.
